      "title": "Cold urticaria, immunodeficiency, and autoimmunity related to PLCG2 deletions",
      "abstract": "MJ Ombrello, EF Remmers, G Sun. N Engl J Med. 2012;366:330–338 ::: ::: To perform Mendelian analysis of 3 families with cold-induced urticaria and identify and elucidate immunologic pathways and mechanisms. ::: ::: Three families with a dominantly inherited complex of cold-induced urticaria, antibody deficiency, and susceptibility to infection and autoimmunity. ::: ::: Immunophenotyping, including flow cytometry, analysis of serum immunoglobulins and autoantibodies, lymphocyte stimulation, and enzymatic assays, was used. …"
